      <title>花旗：欧洲股市 2024 年将出现个位数涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-03/europe-stocks-to-see-single-digit-gains-in-2024-citi-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团的埃莉斯·巴多伊表示，她预计欧洲股市到今年年底将温和上涨，并补充说企业面临着国际风格的市场。 “比起美国，我更愿意将中国视为增长源泉，”她告诉彭博电视台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-03/europe-stocks-to-see-single-digit-gains-in-2024-citi-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 09:18:49 GMT</pubDate>
